<item>
            <title>[LU-14989] Access to encrypted file&apos;s xattrs</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14989</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Because encryption context is cached as an xattr, it prevents other xattrs to be later stored in the xattr cache, thus blocking access to those xattrs for an encrypted file.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
